Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:05.19,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'd been thinking for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:10.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...whether there's any meaning to a failed love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:17.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Is something that will disappear the same as something that never existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:25.24,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}watashi ga umareta asa no machi yuki no naka ni umoreta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:30.78,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore wa sore wa chiisai te de aozora wo aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:37.41,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:42.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:48.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.70,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:00.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:05.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:12.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:18.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:24.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:36.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:47.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:25.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:30.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:37.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:42.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:48.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.70,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:00.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:05.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:12.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:18.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:24.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:36.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:47.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:56.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:59.77,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.19,clover,,0,0,0,,W-W-What you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just as you heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:09.65,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I love her very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:14.14,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um, s-s-since when...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:16.30,clover,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.25,clover,,0,0,0,,"When", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:23.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Um... I can explain it if you want me to, but take it easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.34,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, um... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.55,clover,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.71,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um, have you t-t-t-told Hagu-chan{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.60,clover,,0,0,0,,I haven't told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.60,clover,,0,0,0,,I think she knows already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.94,clover,,0,0,0,,W-W-W-W-W...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:46.57,sign,,0,0,5,,{\fad(522,0)\fnCalibri\bord2.5\fs30\3c&HEDFBFF&\c&H3C4650&}When are you telling her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, will you speak normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.57,clover,,0,0,0,,I-I'm in shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.29,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean, I never noticed anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:58.44,clover,,0,0,0,,But now that I think about it, Sensei is a man, despite his age...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:08.09,sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H435C6C&\3c&HDCEFF3&\pos(349,214)\fad(400,0)}A man,\N despite his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:01.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I hadn't thought about that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I thought you were completely out of the equation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:08.09,sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(297,130)\c&HE6EDF3&\3c&H665640&}Essentially out\Nof the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:08.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamada-san, your thoughts are flowing right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:12.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I need to go to Hagu-chan and t-t-t-t-t-...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.30,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\fad(439,0)\fnSegoe Print\c&H3D4941&\3c&HEAF5FD&\fs36\frz342.831\move(505,320,511,320,0,1691)}I need to go tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.76,clover,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to go and tell her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.24,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.89,clover,,0,0,0,,But why? What about Spain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.96,clover,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.02,clover,,0,0,0,,W-W-W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.30,clover,,0,0,0,,I just heard from Professor Tange!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:33.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I'm so happy for you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm suffocating...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.37,clover,,0,0,0,,But will you be all right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Taking a sabbatical all of a sudden like this... What about your living expenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see the day when you would worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.55,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:56.57,clover,,0,0,0,,I have various projects to do for some publishers, thanks to my work with Tokudaiji-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.85,clover,,0,0,0,,I can also give art seminars to the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.43,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm tougher than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei... you've finally decided, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:16.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada, thanks for contacting me about Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:24.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I should've contacted you earlier, but I thought I'd just be worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:25.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and thanks for finding Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:30.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.67,clover,,0,0,0,,But I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Did I do something unnecessary again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.41,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:45.14,clover,,0,0,0,,You know, I think it had to turn out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:49.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Or rather, the sequence of events was all leading up to this outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:55.88,clover,,0,0,0,,I thought that Hagu-chan was in love with Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.70,clover,,0,0,0,,She is in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:04.02,clover,,0,0,0,,I think it's a matter of what her purpose in life is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Purpose in life...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:11.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Love is the reason for some, but not for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:20.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan is motivated by her desire to accomplish something... I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Is that more important than love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:30.20,clover,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of which is more important or which is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.02,clover,,0,0,0,,It's not an act of selfishness either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.74,clover,,0,0,0,,She chooses instinctively before she has time to think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.25,clover,,0,0,0,,So you're leaving this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.57,clover,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.27,clover,,0,0,0,,So you've finally decided to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:15.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you for everything, Tange-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:23.61,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm here because I want to be, but it seemed to me like you were stuck without a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:29.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it was difficult for me to watch you after what happened to Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:33.51,clover,,0,0,0,,It seemed like half of you went with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.38,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:42.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I could tell that more and more of you was coming back, ever since you brought that girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Tange-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:50.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Hanamoto, now it's your turn to save that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:54.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Saving her will also save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:03.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I wanted to see you as soon as I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:08.54,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I would've have been sad if you abandoned an important project to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.02,clover,,0,0,0,,No, I would've been upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:12.83,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun stopped me, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.84,clover,,0,0,0,,He scolded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:24.01,clover,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do for them by going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.93,clover,,0,0,0,,It'll just trouble Sensei more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.79,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:31.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.61,clover,,0,0,0,,I've known Sensei for the past six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:41.41,clover,,0,0,0,,The Hanamoto-san that I know is a respectable individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.71,clover,,0,0,0,,He was saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Man, damn it all. That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Can't you say that to my face? Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.90,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:19.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me that you bought out my company's stock and took over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.34,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that I did something to deserve your grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,When did this happen, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.29,thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\t(955,2373,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}W-Wait a second...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.89,clover,,0,0,0,,This will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:39.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay to chop so much of it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.92,clover,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Now the bushes in our yard are ready for the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.35,clover,,0,0,0,,But still, there really must be a God, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:52.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Truly, to think that someone would rent us this large house for next to nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:57.31,clover,,0,0,0,,...as long as we maintain the yard as we found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:03.94,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing you all so much trouble... All because I had my company taken over...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.47,clover,,0,0,0,,No way! This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:16.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm happy... the day has finally arrived when we can all work together again under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.96,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:21.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to enjoy living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Please cheer up, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:31.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:32.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:38.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... Shiroyama... and everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.06,clover,,0,0,0,,This was all your doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:48.11,clover,,0,0,0,,You all knew I would end up like this. So you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Shiroyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:56.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.04,clover,,0,0,0,,It's Kaoru-sama, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Where have you been loafing around for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:09.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Your desk is starting to tilt over on its side from all the unsigned paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:14.25,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll all be waiting for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:21.40,clover,,0,0,0,,And Shinobu-sama said there is something he absolutely must tell you, Kaoru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.74,clover,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kaoru-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:34.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Might you be interested in a system that swindles 190 yen a month, forever, from the upper-class citizens of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:39.16,clover,,0,0,0,,I-If it's for 230 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.21,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll return right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.09,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll be back tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:46.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Please prepare a meeting and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-sama will come flying as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll make arrangements for a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.39,clover,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:53.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.56,clover,,0,0,0,,I bet Matsuda-san will do his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shiroyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.45,clover,,0,0,0,,That one reminds me of Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.87,clover,,0,0,0,,The pigeon? What reminds you of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:24.25,clover,,0,0,0,,That white one has round eyes, good posture, a supple breast, and pink legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:30.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Dr. Satsuki told me that working with clay will be good for my rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.73,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:35.30,clover,,0,0,0,,I also want to learn how to make pottery from Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.66,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to make a pigeon first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.02,clover,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.24,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to give the first one to Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.77,clover,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.69,clover,,0,0,0,,The second one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:50.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to give it to my new mother and her baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Will I make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.90,clover,,0,0,0,,You'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.04,clover,,0,0,0,,The baby will be born in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.08,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Can't you say something better than "Yo"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.56,clover,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Shiroyama, get Shinobu some curry, with extra sauce and meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Shiroyama, what are you crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:51.07,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go work for Peter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:59.35,clover,,0,0,0,,In spite of what I say about him, I actually like that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.30,clover,,0,0,0,,...and his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:07.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean, when the electricity goes out at the studio, they all come out and start swordfighting with beam sabers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:10.97,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, they all seem so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:15.29,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've met an adult as stupid as Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.86,clover,,0,0,0,,And the same goes for his ridiculous company...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.45,clover,,0,0,0,,What about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.87,clover,,0,0,0,,She told me, {\i1}"I'll watch you forever."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.51,clover,,0,0,0,,She's such a strong woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:35.06,clover,,0,0,0,,She immediately saw that I was trying to abandon everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:39.20,clover,,0,0,0,,She told me, {\i1}"Please, don't run away."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.90,clover,,0,0,0,,"Let's get through it together."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.56,clover,,0,0,0,,"You can run away in an instant."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.31,clover,,0,0,0,,But still, isn't it terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:54.04,clover,,0,0,0,,When you're told, {\i1}"I'll watch you forever,"{\i0} you have no choice but to give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:01.94,clover,,0,0,0,,But when I thought about pulling myself together and seeing her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.89,clover,,0,0,0,,...that I want to create something new and show it to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.25,clover,,0,0,0,,...that was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.32,clover,,0,0,0,,...I thought I saw the light in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.58,clover,,0,0,0,,It's morning already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.24,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:20.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:26.78,clover,,0,0,0,,I think I finally understand what Dad was trying to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:29.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.86,clover,,0,0,0,,And so, in the spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:40.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan and I, after she was discharged from the hospital, graduated from Hamabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:41.61,sign,,0,0,0,,Graduation - Hamadayama College of Art
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:47.41,clover,,0,0,0,,And now, in commemoration of Hagu-chan and Takemoto-kun's graduation, and Takemoto-kun's departure to Morioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:57.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Is this it? The TV show that Peter Lucas and Morita-san appeared in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I heard it's a special documentary for a movie channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san sure seems like a movie star now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:06.07,clover,,0,0,0,,He seems so full of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.89,clover,,0,0,0,,No... he hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:15.49,clover,,0,0,0,,So you've finally decided, Morita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.07,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I was just thinking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.57,clover,,0,0,0,,By the way, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.50,clover,,0,0,0,,What time was your bullet train tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's at 9:30 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.36,clover,,0,0,0,,What about your apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.58,clover,,0,0,0,,I've already cleaned it out. It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.14,clover,,0,0,0,,Then, where are you staying tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's staying in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.38,clover,,0,0,0,,This being the last time and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.42,clover,,0,0,0,,The last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.17,clover,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Hagu, c-can you go buy some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! Ice cream! Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.06,clover,,0,0,0,,T-Takemoto! P-Please go with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.82,clover,,0,0,0,,O-O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.84,clover,,0,0,0,,That was close... I was about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:06.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Me three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.10,clover,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:23.14,clover,,0,0,0,,I think the temples that you will fix are fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:28.68,clover,,0,0,0,,I've always been watching you making that tower, so I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:33.17,clover,,0,0,0,,You aren't careless nor do you cut corners, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.39,clover,,0,0,0,,You'll fix them with all of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.71,clover,,0,0,0,,That's why I think the temples are fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:42.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.93,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll try my hardest, too. I want my efforts to match yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.74,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fix my right hand for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.08,clover,,0,0,0,,If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:58.12,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to return anything to Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.54,clover,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.96,clover,,0,0,0,,The thing that Sensei is looking for isn't up to you to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.76,clover,,0,0,0,,...but it's something Sensei is trying to find on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.97,clover,,0,0,0,,And I believe that Sensei is a man who can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.73,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:23.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:33.07,clover,,0,0,0,,A six-tatami room with no bath, ten minute walk from the college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Built twenty-eight years ago, rent 34,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.92,clover,,0,0,0,,The morning sun is bright since it faces east.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Today, I leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:56.48,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yamabiko #47 to Morioka will be departing from track 21 shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Geez. It's completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Quiet isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.90,clover,,0,0,0,,It's a little lonely thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.05,clover,,0,0,0,,H-Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:21.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun, I'm glad I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:17.46,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nameraka ni sunda sawa no mizu wo\NShowering myself without hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:23.17,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tamerau koto mo naku nagashikomi\N...with the crystal-clear water from the brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:29.17,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}natsukashiku kaoru gogo no kaze wo\NI laugh to myself wistfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:34.99,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nureta kubisuji ni ukete warau\N...as I feel the afternoon wind on my wet neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:40.70,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nousagi no hashirinukeru sama mo\NThe sight of the wild rabbit running through...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:46.43,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sasayuri hikaru kana no sugata mo\NThe sight of the brilliant Japanese lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.22,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:46.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,These...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:52.38,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}yozora ni matataku hoshi no mure mo\NAnd the sight of the clusters of stars shining in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,All of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:56.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please... Please let there be as much happiness as possible for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:58.39,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}atarimae ni boku no me no naka ni\N...all reside naturally inside my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:08.09,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanarazu todoku to shinjite ita maboroshi\NThose illusions that I believed would reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.19,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.65,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd been wondering all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:17.52,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}koboba ni mamireta nega no machi wa tsudzuku\N...continue to be drowned in the noise of the monochromatic city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:14.73,clover,,0,0,0,,...whether there's any meaning to a failed love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:21.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Is something that will disappear the same as something that will never existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:35.80,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sayonara sayonara itsu no hi ni ka kimi to mata aetara ii na\NFarewell, farewell... I hope I'll see you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.20,clover,,0,0,0,,There is a meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.00,clover,,0,0,0,,There was a meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.35,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.31,clover,,0,0,0,,...that I fell in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.31,clover,,0,0,0,,...I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:21:04.20,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa\NIt would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:14.67,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba\N...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.17,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni\N...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:26.91,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi\NAt the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:40.75,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru\N...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.44,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte\NDespite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.34,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte\N...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:50.67,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru\N...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:58.61,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda\NJust how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:59.87,clover,,0,0,0,,As time passes, the day will come when everything will fade to memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:02.66,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}kakekondenda\NHow long...?
